        {
            "title": "「誰給你權力把我們拖入戰爭」 向來親美的阿聯酋商界對川普愈發不滿",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"「誰給你權力把我們拖入戰爭」 向來親美的阿聯酋商界對川普愈發不滿\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sxupyVXmqHh7VgD109NQ9Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/2f1d2850-1989-11f1-af8e-a0a61b700b9a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">「誰給你權力把我們拖入戰爭」 向來親美的阿聯酋商界對川普愈發不滿</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AA%B0%E7%B5%A6%E4%BD%A0%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%8A%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%8B%96%E5%85%A5%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD-%E5%90%91%E4%BE%86%E8%A6%AA%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%98%BF%E8%81%AF%E9%85%8B%E5%95%86%E7%95%8C%E5%B0%8D%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%84%88%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF-131003773.html",
