        {
            "title": "Wedbush下調The Trade Desk評級,稱市場高估OpenAI合作影響",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Linaol8dBpjX_6D2P1VUNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6H0CU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Wedbush Securities分析師認為,The Trade Desk股價因與OpenAI潛在合作的樂觀情緒而漲幅過大,該機構週五在給客戶的報告中將該股評級下調至表現不佳。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Wedbush分析師Alicia Reese表示,在有報導稱<span><span><span><span>The Trade Desk</span></span></span></span>可能協助將OpenAI旗下ChatGPT相關的廣告庫存變現後,該股飆升約18%,該機構因此將評級從中性下調。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-69874dda-e6af-3e64-a553-7cb459f70a4b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Reese補充說,她\"不認為傳聞中的交易所帶來的增量價值能支撐目前的股價\",她認為市場大幅高估了這項合作對短期財務的貢獻。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構承認,這項交易從長遠來看可能具有戰略重要性,稱其為\"對抗AI搜尋蠶食的重要長期戰略舉措\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,Reese警告稱,此次股價上漲反映的是\"敘事驅動的’頭條效應’\",而非基本面經濟效益。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Wedbush的估算,這項合作將產生相對有限的財務收益。其分析預測\"2027年預期增量EBITDA僅為4,200萬美元\",而與此消息相關的近20億美元市值增長意味著\"約53倍的EBITDA倍數\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">營收貢獻同樣顯得有限。Wedbush估計,The Trade Desk在2026年可能獲得3,100萬至7,700萬美元的營收,2027年則為5,600萬至1.4億美元,僅佔\"TTD預計營收基數的1-4%\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構還警告了較長期的結構性風險,包括如果OpenAI最終開發自己的廣告平台,可能會出現去中介化的情況。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Wedbush表示:\"隨著OpenAI的成熟,我們預計它將不可避免地建立專有的內部DSP。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管存在這些擔憂,該機構仍維持該股23美元的目標價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/wedbush%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BFthe-trade-desk%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E7%A8%B1%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%AB%98%E4%BC%B0openai%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-175216887.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-07 01:57:34",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大摩:能源衝擊對亞洲影響最大,歐美次之",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QyLGEbGs.N3gRP1XL7u6hA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA60168_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根士丹利\">摩根士丹利</a>分析師表示,油價飆升將對亞洲經濟體造成最沉重的打擊,而歐洲和美國面臨的經濟影響則相對溫和。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行在給客戶的報告中指出,由於依賴進口能源,亞洲地區尤其容易受到衝擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利寫道:\"亞洲是在經濟增長方面最易受影響的地區,因為該地區嚴重依賴進口能源\",並估計\"油價持續上漲10美元/桶預計將使該地區GDP增長率降低20至30點子\"。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a383f5d3-3c47-390a-9712-c6483cbacc7b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行補充說,整個地區的通脹影響可能仍在可控範圍內,指出\"在完全傳導的情況下,全區CPI影響約為0.4個百分點\",部分被一些經濟體的補貼和管制價格所抵消。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相比之下,預計美國受到的影響相對有限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利認為,石油衝擊將\"暫時推高整體通脹\",但歷史經驗表明,對核心通脹的傳導有限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價持續上漲10%將在數月內為整體通脹增加約30點子,之後逐漸消退。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行還指出,除非能源價格上漲顯著削弱消費或勞動力市場,否則對美國經濟增長的更廣泛衝擊可能仍然溫和。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲面臨更為複雜的滯脹動態。摩根士丹利估計,在歐元區,油價持續上漲10美元/桶將\"使GDP下降約15點子,同時推高通脹約40點子\",影響將在數個季度內擴散。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">總體而言,摩根士丹利表示,能源衝擊的主要風險可能是\"波動性和不確定性增加,而非大規模的增長衝擊\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E6%91%A9-%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E5%B0%8D%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7-%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E6%AC%A1%E4%B9%8B-164114760.html",
